# Environment variables for this service are defined in the root .env.example.
# See: ../.env.example
#
# Docker: no action needed — docker-compose.yml injects vars automatically.
# Local dev: python-dotenv's find_dotenv() traverses up automatically,
#            so a .env at the repo root is picked up without any symlink.
#            Run `make setup` from the repo root if you prefer a local copy.
